SUMMARY:Easter at Plain & Fancy Farm
DESCRIPTION:All-you-can-eat family-style dining for Easter.\n\n\nJoin us this Easter on Sunday April 5\, 2026 for a scrumptious family-style Easter themed meal.  Enjoy a tasty all-you-can-eat meal served family-style that includes Lancaster County favorites and traditional Easter items. All Inclusive Pricing!  \nCALL (717) 768-4400 to make your reservation. \nAll-Inclusive Price\n$46 per adult| $23 per child (ages 4-12) \nIncludes non-alcoholic beverage\, tax and gratuity \nMain Entrees: Fried Chicken\, Ham with Pineapple Sauce\, and Spinach Artichoke Stuffed Pork Loin \nSides: Caprese Tomato Salad with Creamy Pesto Dressing\, Mashed Potatoes with Gravy\, Browned Buttered Noodles\, Butternut Squash & Potato Gratin\, Peas with Crispy Bacon\, Roasted Broccoli Florets with Lemon Herb Butter\, and Rolls with Butter \nDesserts: Strawberry Jam Cheesecake and Carrot Cake \n\nLooking for an Easy at Home Easter Meal? Try our Easter To-Go!\nIt is a meal for 4 for just $100 including tax. \n \nMeal includes: \n\n3 Pounds of Oven Roasted Ham\nCaprese Tomato Salad with Creamy Pesto Dressing\n1 Quart of Brown Buttered Noodles\n1 Quart of Mashed Potatoes\, plus gravy.\n1 Quart of Peas with Crispy Bacon\n1 Quart of Roasted Broccoli Florets with Lemon Herb Butter\n8 Dinner Rolls\n4 Slices of Strawberry Jam Cheesecake\n\nUpgrade your Easter at home by adding 1 lb of prime rib for $40 to your Easter-To-Go. \nNo substitutions. Call (717) 419-1337 to place your order for Easter To-Go. Please place your order by 12N by 3/30/2026.
URL:https://lancasterpa.com/events-calendar/195317/
LOCATION:Smokehouse BBQ & Brews\, 3121 Old Philadelphia Pike\, Bird in Hand\, 17505\, United States
CATEGORIES:Bird-in-Hand,Easter Events,Food & Beverage Events,Smokehouse BBQ & Brews
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://lancasterpa.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Smokehouse-Event-Easter.png
