SUMMARY:Into the Woods - Dinner & a Show at Log Cabin Restaurant
DESCRIPTION:The Log Cabin restaurant is proud to partner with the Ephrata Performing Arts Center (EPAC) to offer guests a seamless dinner-and-a-show experience on opening night of their 2026 shows. \nBegin your evening at 5PM with a curated 3-course dinner at The Log Cabin. After dinner\, make your way to the Ephrata Performing Arts Center to enjoy the excitement of opening night starting at 7:30PM. Relax\, enjoy each course\, and arrive at EPAC with plenty of time before the show. \nDinner: The Log Cabin\, 11 Lehoy Forest Dr\, Leola\, PA 17540 \nShow: Ephrata Performing Arts Center (EPAC)\, 320 Cocalico St\, Ephrata\, PA 17522\n \nInto The Woods at Ephrata Performing Arts Center
