SUMMARY:The Temptations & The Four Tops - American Music Theatre
DESCRIPTION:Often referred to as American Music Royalty\, The Temptations are world-renowned superstars of entertainment\, revered for their phenomenal catalog of music and prolific career.  Thanks to their fine-tuned choreography\, and even finer harmonies\, The Temptations became one of the most successful acts to record for Motown Records.  During the group’s six-decade career\, these Grammy winners have charted numerous #1 hits including “My Girl\,” “Ain’t Too Proud to Beg\,” “Get Ready\,” “Just My Imagination\,” and “Papa Was a Rollin’ Stone\,” among many others. \nThe Four Tops teamed up in high school and spent over four decades without a single personnel change to become one of Motown’s most consistent hit makers.  “Baby I Need Your Loving\,” “I Can’t Help Myself (Sugar Pie\, Honey Bunch)\,” “Reach Out (I’ll Be There)\,” “Standing in the Shadows of Love\,” and “Ain’t No Woman (Like the One I’ve Got)” are just some of their classic hits. \n\nCome Explore Our Lancaster Theaters and the Arts\n\n\nLive Theater\nLive Entertainment\nLive Music\n\n\n\nDinner Theaters\nMurder Mysteries\nThings To Do\n\n\n\nArtisan Collectives\nArt Galleries\nEvents Calendar
URL:https://lancasterpa.com/events-calendar/temptations-four-tops-american-music-theatre/
LOCATION:American Music Theatre\, 2425 Lincoln Highway East\, Lancaster\, PA\, 17602\, United States
CATEGORIES:Concert,Entertainment,Musical Events,Route 30
