SUMMARY:Rawlinsville Annual Mud Sale
DESCRIPTION:April 10th and 11th is our 2026 mud sale! \nApril 10th at 5:00pm we will be selling crafts\, flowers and shrubs\, and tools. \nApril 11th we will be offering crafts\, quilts\, flowers\, lawn and garden\, groceries\, building materials\, new and used tools\, sporting goods\, and much much more! \nGood food will be available both days! \nThis event happens on the second Saturday of April every year. \n\nMud Sales are a unique Lancaster County tradition to raise funds for local volunteer fire companies. See our complete schedule of Lancaster County mud sales. \nPlease Note: Many of the Fire Companies holding mud sales can always use extra help on the days they receive items and the day of the event.  It takes a LOT of labor to put on a mud sale. \n  \n 
URL:https://lancasterpa.com/events-calendar/rawlinsville-annual-mud-sale-2/2026-04-10/
LOCATION:Rawlinsville Volunteer Fire Company\, 33 Martic Heights Dr.\, Holtwood\, PA\, 17532\, United States
